title: Mortal Kombat 1: Li Mei And Guest Characters Discussion | SDCC 2023
description:
At San Diego Comic-Con 2023, NetherRealm’s Ed Boon and actress Kelly Hu join us to discuss Li Mei, and the addition of Homelander, Omni-Man, and Peacemaker in the upcoming Kombat Pack in Mortal Kombat 1. This will be the first time Li Mei is playable in the Mortal Kombat franchise.

#mortalkombat #gamespot #gaming
